{"tid":1546062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然反送中可以打國際線，點解地鐵唔打國際線？","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:42:39.000Z","uid":126839,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"66ca6387c39cd30b59b85da1ff9181483428a80f","tid":1546062,"uid":126839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:39:50.000Z","msg":"上網由佢個公司業務入面睇到：<br />\n<br />\n海外業務方面，公司在<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英國</span></span></strong></div>參與營運及管理TfL Rail (未來將易名為『伊利莎伯綫』)、聯合營運及管理西南部鐵路專營權，亦分別在<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲和瑞典</span></span></strong>營運及管理<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲墨爾本</span></span></strong>鐵路、<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">瑞典斯德哥爾摩</span></span></strong>地鐵、Stockholm Pendelt&aring;g鐵路服務及來往<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">斯德哥爾摩和哥德堡</span></span></strong>的城際列車服務MTR Express。二零一四年九月，港鐵公司參與組成的Northwest Rapid Transit 財團獲批<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲悉尼</span></span></strong>西北鐵路綫的營運、列車及系統公私聯營合約。此外，公司的顧問服務已覆蓋至亞洲、澳洲以及中東多個城市。<br />\n<br />\n既然澳洲奶共，但係都仲有我爺大英同瑞典兩地可以攻略！<br />\n透過文宣/登報等，將721 及831發生係地鐵既恐襲放係外國面前，希望佢地正視地鐵既管理及營運質素，什至施壓！<br />\n<br />\n呢個方向有無得做？"},{"pid":"2a784fa0656e7715517be0a9b9be64fc367f6e64","tid":1546062,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:40:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0973f335220d8c1c46a7c91fd1d1883d41199c4","tid":1546062,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn